@NODE Introduction_and_legal_stuff "Introduction and legal stuff"

    The Program enables you to use a digitizertablet from Summagraphic
    with your Commodore Amiga. The amigamousepointer is controlled by
    the driver for providing compatibility to nearly every program.

@{" legal stuff " Link legal_stuff}
@ENDNODE

